title: 798. Odds Teams In the First Round Take a QB
itunes:title: 798. Odds Teams In the First Round Take a QB
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the news of the rule change passing which now guarantees a possession in overtime for both teams in the playoffs. Then for the rest of the podcast, the pair go through each team in the first round that could take a quarterback and give a percentage chance of them taking a quarterback.

Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
